{"tid":2020091,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"中史教書可以拎《古惑仔4》做例子：「點解屯門叫屯門唔叫江門廈門？」","createTime":"2020-05-16T18:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T12:33:00.000Z","uid":7439,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"964a2109a0d0350285c11941ad2b4e12896b02e0","tid":2020091,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:26:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqQX0Rr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqQX0Rr.jpg&h=3426fab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hKKh0Rt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhKKh0Rt.png&h=7a4813f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yRoyhUFVeDs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyRoyhUFVeDs&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e617Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=0c617d6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yRoyhUFVeDs</a><br />\n係唐朝唔係清朝，不過古惑仔係咁上下見識⋯⋯"},{"pid":"441f9482f1103de036e5da6c91854bfac56a5522","tid":2020091,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:28:54.000Z","msg":"《新唐書》<br />\n卷四十三上 志第三十三上 地理七<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>嶺南採訪使<br />\n　　廣州南海郡，中，都督府。土貢：銀、藤簟、竹蓆、荔支、皮、鱉甲、蚺蛇膽、石斛、沈香、甲香、詹糖香。戶四萬二千二百三十五，口二十二萬一千五百。縣十三：有府二，曰綏南、番禺。<span style=\"color: red;\">有經略軍，屯門鎮兵。</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1533c614e0f2a834444c991f0d1050ed447d1521","tid":2020091,"uid":196050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:29:15.000Z","msg":"所以係大唐領土唔係中華人民共和國領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8f7eb7dc7b78843295a276bc3b03af4aa006da","tid":2020091,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1533c614e0f2a834444c991f0d1050ed447d1521","tid":2020091,"uid":196050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:29:15.000Z","msg":"所以係大唐領土唔係中華人民共和國領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:32:01.000Z","msg":"明朝大戰葡仔<br />\n<br />\n吳瑗：「屯門臨不測之海，風濤險惡，寇恃火炮為長技，虐焰張甚，士或憚行，公毅然身率之。」<br />\n<br />\n汪鋐 《駐節南頭喜鄉眷吳瑗鄭志銳劃攻屯門彜之策賦之》<br />\n<blockquote>轔轔車馬出城東，攬轡欣逢二老同。<br />\n萬里奔馳筋力在，一生精潔鬼神通。<br />\n灶田撥鹵當秋日，漁艇牽篷向晚風。<br />\n回首長歌無盡興，天高海闊月明中。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"83a92b58a4be56fc69fee1f83f01529c112b2043","tid":2020091,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1533c614e0f2a834444c991f0d1050ed447d1521","tid":2020091,"uid":196050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:29:15.000Z","msg":"所以係大唐領土唔係中華人民共和國領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T18:35:43.000Z","msg":"自古以來系列<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n　　安南中都護府，本交趾郡，武德五年曰交州，治交趾。調露元年曰安南都護府，至德二載曰鎮南都護府，大曆三年復為安南。寶曆元年徙治宋平。土貢：蕉、檳榔、鮫革、蚺蛇膽、翠羽。戶二萬四千二百三十，口九萬九千六百五十二。縣八：有經略軍。<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b77cc7344fe3755a177f5e579c5a220c4ff2ecfe","tid":2020091,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:03:23.000Z","msg":"所以屯門係, 九龍港島唔係"},{"pid":"c424b6205a2dbf972b3586c94e9722ccad70e3b8","tid":2020091,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9509d4fb42dbc9a2efcaf037a271bd0bd62a481c","tid":2020091,"uid":259532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T19:59:17.000Z","msg":"我支那就係夠薑夠雷夠蹋馬"},{"pid":"851b020781fd4e862fd085d453d9b57d179427ed","tid":2020091,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T20:02:28.000Z","msg":"上多連登，中學生都知正史啦，封埋上網丫笨"},{"pid":"331801b2e2e20e576523298815a29f2b10c6eebc","tid":2020091,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T20:04:03.000Z","msg":"即係無講秦朝係侵略百越領土啦？"},{"pid":"6c18dd8e5c90cadbdd9e2493a7d28ae7fa83b711","tid":2020091,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T20:15:02.000Z","msg":"自古以